          <Base:Description type="brief">
             ornate heart shaped music box
          </Base:Description>
          <Base:Description type="examine">
             This is an ornately decorated clockwork music box, crafted into the shape of a heart.  The bottom and sides of the body are clear glass intricately etched with vines and rosebuds and decorated with silver roses.  An inscription has been etched into the glass.  The body is held together by a delicate gold frame which also supports a mirror top which has been designed to represent a dancing floor.  Two small figurines hold each other in a dancing embrace.  The left side of the music box contains a winding key.
          </Base:Description>
          <Base:Description type="look">
             A dainty, heart shaped music box.  A gold frame holds delicately etched glass decorated with silver roses.  The top of the box is an etched mirror and support to small figurines.
          </Base:Description>
        </Base:Descriptions>
